## Description {#details}

This format is a simple text format that&#39;s suitable for test data.

The header is a custom format starting with <code>:</code> per line to indicate which codegen data is recorded. <code>#</code> is used to indicate a comment. The subsequent data is a YAML format per each codegen data in order. Currently, it only has a function outlined hash tree.
